  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a continental buffet breakfast with additional hot options, served between 6:30-10am. Dinner consists of three course evening meals with choice of menu, served between 7:00-9:30pm. Earlier meal times for children are available on request.</p>
<p>Restaurant 'La Table du Refuge' serves a la carte French cuisine.</p>
<p>Packed lunches can be booked and paid for locally.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
