  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Les Aiglons is a newly refurbished, stylish and modern hotel with excellent facilities, unbeatable levels of service and cuisine and a friendly, relaxed atmosphere. Benefiting from a superb location in <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, the hotel features extensive spa and wellness facilities making this hotel a first-class destination.</p>
<h2>Fun for families</h2>
<p>Hotel Les Aiglons is a fantastic choice if you're hoping to bring your family on your annual skiing trip. There is a designated children's play area available during French school holidays, as well as a selection of wooden board games in the hotel lounge. The hotel also offers an escape game available within the premises and it is completely free of charge! Take on the adventure and attempt to solve the hotels mystery with your loved ones. </p>
<h2>Great location</h2>
<p>Found in the centre of Chamonix, Hotel Les Aiglons is situated at the footsteps of the Aiguille du Midi with a ski bus stop opposite the building. Not only that but the hotel has an integrated ski shop meaning access to equipment is quick and easy and any problems can get sorted straight away. We can't forget to mention the incredible views that come with it's placement - the terrace overlooks the magnificent Mont Blanc, Brévent and Les Aiguilles mountains. </p>
<h2>First-class spa treatments </h2>
<p>The hotel has an appealing range of relaxation facilities such as sauna and Turkish bath cabins in the garden, an outdoor heated swimming pool and fitness room. When staying at Hotel Les Aiglons, you'll receive free access to the spa facilities and have the opportunity to purchase a range of massages and beauty treatments. All treatments use natural mineral based products, perfect for rejuvenating and recharging after a day of snow sports.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
